class RsiOscillator(TrailingStrategy):
    """
    Buy when we cross the lower bound to the upside
    hold until we get stopped out
    """

    rsi_window = 14
    lower_bound = 70
    stop_range = 10

    def init(self):
        super().init()
        super().set_trailing_sl(self.stop_range)
        self.rsi = self.I(ta.rsi, self.data.Close.s, self.rsi_window)

    def next(self):
        super().next()
        price = self.data.Close[-1]

        if len(self.trades) == 0:
            if crossover(self.rsi, self.lower_bound):
                self.buy()
                # self.buy(size=1, sl=price * 0.99, tp=price * 1.02)

bt = Backtest(df, RsiOscillator, commission=0.0002)

stats = bt.run(
            rsi_window = 21,
            lower_bound = 40,
            stop_range = 5,
        )

print(stats)
bt.plot()

class RsiOscillator(TrailingStrategy):
    """
    Buy when we cross the lower bound to the upside
    hold until we get stopped out
    """

    rsi_window = 14
    lower_bound = 70
    stop_range = 10

    def init(self):
        super().init()
        super().set_trailing_sl(self.stop_range)
        self.rsi = self.I(ta.rsi, self.data.Close.s, self.rsi_window)

    def next(self):
        super().next()
        price = self.data.Close[-1]

        if len(self.trades) == 0:
            if crossover(self.rsi, self.lower_bound):
                self.buy(size=1, sl=price * 0.99, tp=price * 1.02)

bt = Backtest(df, RsiOscillator, commission=0.0002)

stats = bt.run(
            rsi_window = 21,
            lower_bound = 40,
            stop_range = 5,
        )

print(stats)
bt.plot()
